events.title: Tauren Wells & Danny Gokey - The Takeback Tour
events.location: Birmingham, Alabama, United States Of America
events.description: Don't miss the chance to catch Tauren Wells and Danny Gokey with special guest Ryan Ellis live on The Takeback Tour this Fall, hitting 12 cities across the nation! Experience nights filled with contagious energy and heartfelt worship, designed to uplift not only the church but the community beyond. Get ready to be moved and inspired by their chart-topping hits including "Known," "Hills and Valleys," "Haven't Seen It Yet," and "Tell Your Heart to Beat Again," as well as some brand new songs! Grab your tickets now and be part of these unforgettable nights!
